{"tid":2317861,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"支爆！支那五大銀行前3季獲利大幅衰退8.73% 營運壓力增","createTime":"2020-12-09T01:55:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-09T03:17:31.000Z","uid":32511,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"a9fbcc4adf5b5eeff719667cb4de9c4e25b4ab36","tid":2317861,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T01:55:28.000Z","msg":"根據中國工商、中國農業、中國建設、中國銀行及交通銀行等5大銀行集團的財報，今年<br />\n前3季的稅後淨利（歸屬母公司股東淨利，下同）合計為7982.65億元人民幣（下同），年<br />\n減率8.73%。<br />\n <br />\n其中中國工商銀行淨利為2286.75億元（年減率9.15%），排名第1；排名第2是中國建設銀<br />\n行（2058.32億元，年減率8.66%）；排名第3是中國農業銀行（1653.35億元，年減率<br />\n8.49%）；排名第4是中國銀行（1457.11億元，年減率8.69%）；排名第5是交通銀行（<br />\n527.12億元，年減率12.36%）。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://reurl.cc/zz94oV\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Freurl.cc%2Fzz94oV&d=If5g8ybbdlMRYcYioqq3W1UwqJDRuBhX9JYyxoGH6Hk%3D&h=12780b66\" target=\"_blank\">https://reurl.cc/zz94oV</a>"},{"pid":"dc6fbce3def5097059658d6b376289660fd6c01f","tid":2317861,"uid":51271,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T02:00:16.000Z","msg":"唔怕，有香港國際凍結中心回血"},{"pid":"cc0b0f0ac93c23e1806b8b0fb9fcb80787042a90","tid":2317861,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T02:00:25.000Z","msg":"又FF支爆 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"157de45d78189a2efe9bd8c1dbbee971e0821001","tid":2317861,"uid":62749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T02:02:00.000Z","msg":"拎晒去填數"},{"pid":"e6b967e214adae98c6d6ec16c6263d7829ebad52","tid":2317861,"uid":39855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dc6fbce3def5097059658d6b376289660fd6c01f","tid":2317861,"uid":51271,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T02:00:16.000Z","msg":"唔怕，有香港國際凍結中心回血"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T02:02:19.000Z","msg":"大愚抽緊血，好快就有！"},{"pid":"bbd5eeeb3d006a1a410241747a62dfc2867198b5","tid":2317861,"uid":167597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy"